<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kopparakecaripaṉmarkku yāṇṭu Uttamacoḻa<unclear>r</unclear>kku <hi rend="grantha">1<unclear>6</unclear></hi><g type="dash"/>Āvatu A
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṭikaḷ paḻa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>veṭṭaraiyar kaṇṭaṉ maṟavaṉār Aru<supplied reason="omitted">ḷi</supplied> ceyya <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kā<hi rend="grantha">ryya</hi>m Ārāyā niṟ(k)ka Iraṇṭu nakarattārum ciṟi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>yappi maḻa
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vāṭi vaitta poṉ patiṉkaḻañcum koṇṭu Iraṇṭu nakarattārum palicai Iṭṭu vārāniṟkiṉṟa poṉ patiṉkaḻa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>cum <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kā<hi rend="grantha">ryya</hi>m Ārāyāniṉṟa kau<hi rend="grantha">śi</hi>kan nakkan māṟapirāṉ Ārācciyil Ippoṉ patiṉ kaḻañcum vāṅkikoṇṭu
<lb n="7"/>ca<hi rend="grantha">ntradi</hi>ttaval Iravum pakalum Oru nontāviḷa
<lb n="8" break="no"/>kku Erippom Ānom Ittaḷippa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṭṭuṭaiyom Eḻuvom Itu <hi rend="grantha">panmāheśvara rakṣai <g type="ddanda">.</g>§</hi>
</p>

